    <item>
      <title>经济困境持续至新年，中国股市下滑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/chinese-stocks-slide-as-economic-woes-linger-into-new-year</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于投资者准备应对经济不确定性，如制造业数据弱于预期，且预计唐纳德·特朗普上任后将上调关税，中国股市在今年首个交易日下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/chinese-stocks-slide-as-economic-woes-linger-into-new-year</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 04:01:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
