    <item>
      <title>渣打银行：2025年中国需“更积极”地挖掘政策空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/china-needs-policies-to-handle-2025-headwinds-stanchart-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行的丁爽表示，2025 年中国经济“充满不确定性”。他告诉彭博电视台，北京的领导人需要“更加雄心勃勃、更加积极地”利用政策空间来应对贸易关税等外部阻力。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-02/china-needs-policies-to-handle-2025-headwinds-stanchart-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 03:25:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2025 年伊始，关注中国前景，金属价格上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/metals-push-higher-with-focus-on-outlook-in-china-as-2025-opens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[工业金属价格在今年第一个交易日上涨，一项私人调查显示中国制造业正在扩张，投资者正在权衡北京方面在 2025 年出台额外刺激措施的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/metals-push-higher-with-focus-on-outlook-in-china-as-2025-opens</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 03:11:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
